---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | TradeCalc Hub"
  description="TradeCalc Hub privacy policy. We respect your privacy. All calculations run in your browser."
  canonical="/privacy"
>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <div class="content-section">
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> March 2026</p>

    <h2>Summary</h2>
    <p>TradeCalc Hub is a static website. All calculations run entirely in your browser. We do not collect personal information, require accounts, or store your calculation data on any server.</p>

    <h2>What We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> We use Cloudflare Analytics, which collects anonymized, aggregate traffic data (page views, countries, browsers). This does not use cookies or track individual users.</li>
      <li><strong>Advertising:</strong> If ads are displayed, our ad partner (Ezoic) may use cookies to serve relevant ads. You can manage your ad preferences through the consent tool displayed on our site.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>What We Don't Collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>No personal information (name, email, phone)</li>
      <li>No calculation inputs or results</li>
      <li>No location tracking</li>
      <li>No account data (we don't have accounts)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>TradeCalc Hub itself does not set cookies. Third-party services (Ezoic for advertising, Skimlinks/Sovrn for affiliate links) may set cookies. You can control cookies through your browser settings.</p>

    <h2>Donations</h2>
    <p>We offer a voluntary Ko-fi donation button powered by PayPal. If you choose to donate, your payment is processed by Ko-fi and PayPal under their respective privacy policies. We do not receive or store your payment details.</p>

    <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
    <p>Our site may contain affiliate links to retailers (such as Home Depot and Lowe's) managed through Impact.com, as well as product links auto-monetized by Skimlinks and/or Sovrn Commerce. These links help support the site at no cost to you. Each retailer has its own privacy policy.</p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about this policy? Email <strong>reach@tradecalchub.com</strong>.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
